Sundays at SXVIII are all about indulgence, excitement, and joy with the Funday Carnival Brunch — a vibrant feast for all senses. @radisson_blu_mbd @brandtalkindia 
From live food counters and grills to stilt walkers, jugglers, and human statues — the Funday Carnival Brunch is a must-experience for families and foodies alike.
Think colourful décor, cheerful carnival vibes, a lavish buffet, and playful entertainment for both kids and adults — only at Radisson Blu MBD Hotel Noida.
Whether you’re brunching with friends or your little ones, the Funday Carnival Brunch every Sunday has something for everyone to smile about.
